wiki.summary: "Bon Appétit" is a song by American singer Katy Perry featuring American hip hop group Migos. The track is a dance-pop song with sexual double entendres involving food. It was released on April 28, 2017, as the second single from her upcoming fifth studio album. Its music video followed on May 12, 2017, and features Perry being prepared and served by chefs as a meal. Read more on Last.fm.
